# MODULAR SCHOOLING SYSTEM - COMPREHENSIVE CONCEPT DOCUMENT

## üéØ VISION
Transform the Schulungs Compagnon from a single-purpose training tool into a universal, interactive schooling platform where educators can create, manage, and deliver engaging live training sessions on any topic, with persistent access to materials for participants.

---

## üèóÔ∏è SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

### Core Components

#### 1. **Module Creator/Editor (Admin Panel)**
- Visual drag-and-drop interface for building training modules
- Template library with pre-configured layouts
- Real-time preview of client view
- Version control and module history
- Import/Export functionality for sharing modules between installations

#### 2. **Content Management System**
- Hybrid storage approach:
  - **Lightweight data** (text, configs, structure): Local database (SQLite)
  - **Heavy media** (videos, large images, PDFs): Git LFS or cloud storage (GitHub, GitLab, AWS S3)
  - **Offline access**: Service Worker caching for viewed content
- Asset library with tagging and search
- Automatic optimization (image compression, lazy loading)

#### 3. **Live Session Controller**
- Real-time synchronization of active submodule across all clients
- Admin controls for navigation (next/prev, jump to specific submodule)
- Session state persistence (resume capability)
- Participant tracking and engagement metrics

#### 4. **Client Viewer**
- Progressive Web App (PWA) for offline capability
- Responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop, projector)
- Synchronized view with smooth transitions
- Personal notes and bookmarks (local storage)

---

## üì¶ MODULE STRUCTURE

### Hierarchy
```
Training Course
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Module 1 (e.g., "Introduction to AI")
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Submodule 1.1 (Card/Page)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Submodule 1.2 (Card/Page)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Submodule 1.3 (Card/Page)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Module 2 (e.g., "Prompt Engineering")
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Submodule 2.1
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Submodule 2.2
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Module 3 (e.g., "Practical Applications")
```

### Module Metadata
- **Title & Description**
- **Estimated Duration**
- **Prerequisites** (link to other modules)
- **Learning Objectives**
- **Tags/Categories** (for filtering and search)
- **Difficulty Level**
- **Author & Version**
- **Theme Override** (colors, fonts, background)

### Submodule (Card) Properties
- **Layout Template** (see templates below)
- **Content Blocks** (text, media, interactive elements)
- **Transition Effects** (fade, slide, zoom)
- **Duration Estimate** (for pacing)
- **Notes Section** (visible to admin only during live session)
- **Individual Styling** (theme, background image, custom CSS)

---

## üé® SUBMODULE TEMPLATES

### 1. **Title Slide**
- Large centered title
- Subtitle/tagline
- Background image or gradient
- Optional logo placement

### 2. **Content Slide**
- Title bar
- Rich text editor with HTML support
- Sidebar for images/media
- Configurable layout (single column, two column, grid)

### 3. **Media Showcase**
- Full-screen image/video
- Caption overlay
- Gallery mode (swipeable carousel)
- Zoom and pan controls

### 4. **App Gallery** (Your specific use case)
- Scrollable list layout
- Each item contains:
  - Square thumbnail (app screenshot)
  - App name and description
  - Prompt used to create it (expandable)
  - "Open App" button (external link)
  - Feedback buttons: üëç Up / üëé Down / üòê Don't Care
  - Real-time vote counter (visible to admin)
- Filtering options (by rating, category)

### 5. **Interactive Quiz**
- Question types:
  - Multiple choice (single/multiple answers)
  - True/False
  - Short answer (text input)
  - Rating scale (1-5, emoji scale)
  - Drag-and-drop matching
- Live results visualization:
  - Bar charts for multiple choice
  - Pie charts for distribution
  - Word clouds for text responses
- Timer option for timed quizzes
- Correct answer reveal (admin controlled)

### 6. **Word Cloud**
- Prompt/question at top
- Real-time text input from participants
- Live word cloud generation
- Filter profanity/inappropriate words
- Export results as image

### 7. **Live Poll**
- Question with 2-10 options
- Real-time voting
- Results display modes:
  - Hidden (until admin reveals)
  - Live updating
  - Final results only
- Anonymous or tracked voting
- Visualization: bar chart, pie chart, emoji reactions

### 8. **Table/Comparison**
- Responsive data tables
- Sortable columns
- Highlight rows/columns
- Expandable rows for details
- Import from CSV/Excel
- Export functionality

### 9. **Timeline/Process**
- Horizontal or vertical timeline
- Step-by-step process visualization
- Expandable detail cards
- Progress indicator
- Animated transitions between steps

### 10. **Split Screen**
- Two-panel layout
- Before/After comparisons
- Code vs. Output
- Theory vs. Practice
- Draggable divider

### 11. **Embedded Content**
- iFrame support for external content
- YouTube/Vimeo video embed
- CodePen/JSFiddle embed
- Google Forms/Docs embed
- Miro/Mural board embed
- Sandbox mode for security

### 12. **Discussion Board**
- Live Q&A section
- Threaded comments
- Upvoting questions
- Admin can pin/highlight questions
- Moderation controls

### 13. **Resource Library**
- Downloadable files list
- Links to external resources
- Categorized sections
- Search functionality
- Preview for documents

### 14. **Blank Canvas**
- Fully customizable with HTML/CSS
- Code editor for advanced users
- Component library (buttons, cards, etc.)
- Responsive preview

