## üìù CONTENT EDITING

### Rich Text Editor Features
- **Formatting Toolbar**:
  - Bold, Italic, Underline, Strikethrough
  - Headings (H1-H6)
  - Lists (ordered, unordered, checklists)
  - Alignment (left, center, right, justify)
  - Text color and highlight
  - Font family and size
- **Insert Options**:
