  - Images (upload, URL, or from library)
  - Videos (upload or embed)
  - Code blocks (syntax highlighting)
  - Tables
  - Horizontal rules
  - Emojis
  - Math equations (LaTeX support)
- **Advanced Features**:
  - Markdown support (for power users)
  - HTML source editing
  - Undo/Redo with history
  - Find and replace
  - Word count
  - Spell check
  - Auto-save drafts

### Content Blocks System
- Modular content blocks that can be:
  - Dragged and reordered
  - Duplicated
  - Deleted
  - Collapsed/expanded
  - Locked (prevent accidental edits)
- Block types:
  - Text block
  - Image block
  - Video block
  - Audio block
  - Code block
  - Quote block
  - Callout/Alert block
  - Divider block
  - Spacer block
  - Custom HTML block

